HEADWORD: Conning tower
<hw>Con"ning tow"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <sn>1.</sn> <pos>n.</pos>
<def>The shot-proof pilot house of a war vessel.</def>
<mark>[archaic]</mark> ⟦br⟧
